o-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xff1719469149188.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xff1719469149188.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xff1719469149188.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cxq1665703127238\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Hyperlink\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__hyperlink_386872\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This widget defines a hyperlink in a static server page. (To use an image as a hyperlink, use the Image USP widget.)\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__topic_d115148e1_d115149e1_d115150e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115151e1_d115152e1_d115153e1\">XHTML Specification: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"Hyperlink\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115154e1_d115155e1_d115156e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fdp1719467376341.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" title=\"XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.\">&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__topic_d81722e1_d81723e1_d81724e1_d81725e1_d81726e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1089050e72\">\n                       \n Widget Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description/More Information</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pne1665703108090.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pne1665703108090.html\" title=\"In a static server page, exclude the field or entity if it does not need to be sent to the browser.\">Exclude</a></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Exclude the field if it does not need to be sent to the browser.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmf1665703108475.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmf1665703108475.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page.\">Link Text (u_hyperldispl)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Visible text of the link; dynamic</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twd1665703108686.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twd1665703108686.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page.\">Link Value (u_url)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Target URL of the hyperlink; dynamic</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqu1665703109428.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqu1665703109428.html\" title=\"Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded.\">Target Window (u_target)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cxq1665703127238__table_d14144e1_d14145e1_d14146e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Type of window in which the target page appears; dynamic</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__topic_d81727e1_d81728e1_d81729e1_d81730e1_d81731e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1089050e198\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115163e1_d115164e1_d115165e1\">When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code is similar to the following:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-subst name=\"LINK.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"hyperlink\"&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"http://google.nl\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;Google&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;/x-subst&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__topic_d81732e1_d81733e1_d81734e1_d81735e1_d81736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1089050e210\">\n                       \n Dynamic Property Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115169e1_d115170e1_d115171e1\">The dynamic properties of the hyperlink control specify the link text, target URL and window type in which the new page is opened. The actual values can be provided at runtime.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115172e1_d115173e1_d115174e1\">Uniface uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span> ProcScript statement to evaluate the contents of these properties at run time, so you can use field substitutions to generate the desired URL. For example, you can enter the following values in the properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__li_d44000e1_d44001e1_d44002e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115175e1_d115176e1_d115177e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Link Text</span>: <code class=\"ph codeph\">%%LINKTXT.MYENT.MYMODEL%%%</code> to use the contents of the LINKTXT field.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__li_d44003e1_d44004e1_d44005e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115178e1_d115179e1_d115180e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Link Value</span>: <code class=\"ph codeph\">%%LINKVALUE.MYENT.MYMODEL%%%</code> to use the contents of the LINKVALUE field.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__li_d44006e1_d44007e1_d44008e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115181e1_d115182e1_d115183e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Target Window</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">%%TARGETWIN.MYENT.MYMODEL%%%</code> to use the contents of the TARGETWIN\n                  field.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cxq1665703127238__p_d115184e1_d115185e1_d115186e1\">The Hyperlink control uses the <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> ProcScript statement to evaluate these values. Each value is concatenated and inserted in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;A HREF&gt;</code> tag at runtime.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Hyperlink Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Hyperlink This widget defines a hyperlink in a static server page. (To use an image as a hyperlink, use the Image USP widget.) XHTML Specification: <x-subst type=\"Hyperlink\"> For more information, see <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> . Widget Properties Table 1. Widget Properties Property Description/More Information Exclude Exclude the field if it does not need to be sent to the browser. Link Text (u_hyperldispl) Visible text of the link; dynamic Link Value (u_url) Target URL of the hyperlink; dynamic Target Window (u_target) Type of window in which the target page appears; dynamic Description When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code is similar to the following: <x-subst name=\"LINK.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"hyperlink\"> <a href=\"http://google.nl\" target=\"_blank\">Google</a> </x-subst> Copy Dynamic Property Values The dynamic properties of the hyperlink control specify the link text, target URL and window type in which the new page is opened. The actual values can be provided at runtime. Uniface uses the = ProcScript statement to evaluate the contents of these properties at run time, so you can use field substitutions to generate the desired URL. For example, you can enter the following values in the properties: Link Text : %%LINKTXT.MYENT.MYMODEL%%% to use the contents of the LINKTXT field. Link Value : %%LINKVALUE.MYENT.MYMODEL%%% to use the contents of the LINKVALUE field. Target Window %%TARGETWIN.MYENT.MYMODEL%%% to use the contents of the TARGETWIN field. The Hyperlink control uses the = ProcScript statement to evaluate these values. Each value is concatenated and inserted in the <A HREF> tag at runtime. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}